{"TopicId":221685,"ForumId":208,"TopicTitle":"Kerbals can plant flag in the air by standing on vessels [option to plant a flag while on EVA in orbit as well]","CreatedByName":"mattihase","CreatedById":73161,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-21T22:51:34Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"mattihase","CreatedById":73161,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-21T22:51:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0i7-10870H | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0RTX 3070 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E16GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis doesn\u0027t really achieve much as flags don\u0027t seem to have physics yet but it does look pretty weird\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/6WaMfacT4SM?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022flag glitch\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-31T12:44:08Z\u0022 title=\u002212/31/2023 12:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 31\u0022\u003EDecember 31, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Spicat\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bedkow","CreatedById":231680,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-31T12:15:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Emaneuver-node related | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Win 10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0i7-10000k | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0rtx 3070 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32gb\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOption to plant a flag is enabled while on EVA in orbit. The Kerbal has to be attached to the craft with their magnetic boots. See picture for example. After clicking the button, Kerbal performs the animation but without the flag. The option disappears for the Kerbal afterwards.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, shortly after performing the action, Kerbal got slingshot with extreme speed from the vessel they were standing on. Flight report shows no significant Gs experienced by Kerbal. Not sure if it is related to the flag animation but I\u0027ll include a screenshot with how altitude changed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/monthly_2023_12/screen1.JPG.fb0884f03b25ac97d3305c6bd81739a0.JPG\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ipslightbox=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/monthly_2023_12/screen2.JPG.4bca8de275c232b0eb0b1cd089ccfac7.JPG\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ipslightbox=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cstyle type=\u0022text/css\u0022\u003E\r\n.ipsImage {\r\nwidth: 900px !important;\r\n}\u003C/style\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-31T12:44:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/231680-bedkow/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022231680\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/231680-bedkow/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Bedkow\u003C/a\u003E, merged your bug report.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jeq","CreatedById":172375,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-31T19:41:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbals can also take surface sample while standing on their vessel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}